6 named Louisiana Outstanding Log Truck Driver of the Year; does hereby recognize his
7 dedicated service as a log truck owner-operator; and does hereby extend enduring
8 appreciation for his tireless efforts in the performance of safe and efficient log truck driving
9 practices.
